headline: 2 Reasons to Like HUBB and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Hubbell has gotten torched over the last six months - since October 2024, its stock price has dropped 22.3% to $332.12 per share. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
